        <div class="content admin-panel"><div>
            <h1>Main Admin Panel</h1>
            <h2>Features:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><b>Add a new hotel:</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Input fields: Hotel name, logo (file upload), and address.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><b>Display all registered hotels in a table:</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Columns: Hotel Name, Address, Logo, and Actions.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><b>Generate a unique QR code for each hotel:</b>
                    <ul>
                        <li>QR codes open hotel-specific landing pages when scanned.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div></div>
        <div class="content guest-page"><div>
            <h1>Guest Landing Page</h1>
            <h2>Features:</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Displays hotel details (name, logo, address).</li>
                <li>Guest form includes:
                    <ul>
                        <li>Full Name</li>
                        <li>Mobile Number</li>
                        <li>Address</li>
                        <li>Purpose of Visit (Dropdown: Business, Personal, Tourist)</li>
                        <li>Stay Dates (From and To)</li>
                        <li>Email ID</li>
                        <li>ID Proof Number</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li>After submission, show a "Thank You" page and save guest details in the database.</li>
            </ul>
        </div></div>
